{"id":"8464","user":{"id":"101860","nickname":"四片叶de三叶吖","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FqcR23gyTBxqpGDVypZpJe8hw4uq","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】第六课—BOX2.0细解斗拱","content":"<p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhwltmzVw_lAQfXU0YrC5x0lejiW\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; Hi~~&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font color=\"#c0c0c0\"> （星空改水墨了，哈哈）</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 又与大家见面啦~</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 首先祝大家元旦快乐<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/36/gza_thumb.gif\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 还记得，上上节课所分析的中国建筑吗？我们曾简单的分析了斗拱，其实斗拱的知识远不止于此，今天让我们重新了解一下斗拱吧~<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d9/dizzya_thumb.gif\"><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d9/dizzya_thumb.gif\"><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d9/dizzya_thumb.gif\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"4\">&nbsp;dǒu&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;gǒng&nbsp; &nbsp; </font>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"7\">斗&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;拱&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</font>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"4\">什么是斗拱？：</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 中国建筑特有的一种结构。在立柱和横梁交接处，从柱顶上加的一层层探出成弓形的承重结构叫拱，拱与拱之间垫的方形木块叫斗，合称斗拱。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmzE00mIA-Mx6sKEw-_Ej_0WeCyN\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<font size=\"5\"> 斗拱的作用：</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 荷载作用 　</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 位于柱与梁之间，由屋面和上层构架传下来的荷载，要通过斗拱传给柱子，再由柱传到基础，因此，它起着承上启下，传递荷载的作用。666~&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 增大距离&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 它向外出挑，可把最外层的桁檀挑出一定距离，使建筑物出檐更加深远，造形更加优美、壮观。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 装饰作用&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 后来的斗拱逐渐变为装饰，也是区别建筑等级的标志。越高贵的建筑斗拱越复杂、繁华。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 抗震作用&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 榫卯结合是抗震的关键。中国古建筑屋顶挑檐采用斗拱形式的较之没有斗拱的，在同样的地震烈度下抗震能力要强得多。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">斗拱的名称：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">以后看到这些不要方~~~</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FvtnL-CfEmbfKuyYsh0gy8zguude\">方~</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">斗拱的种类：</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 柱头科斗拱：</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 柱头科斗拱是位于柱头部位的斗拱。是明清时期的主要承重斗拱，其受力构件的截面尺寸比其它的斗拱同类构件截面尺寸大。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 平身科斗拱 ：</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 平身科斗拱是清式斗拱的一个分科。置于两柱之间，均匀放置在额枋、平板枋上面的斗拱。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 角科斗拱 ：</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 角科斗拱是置于建筑物转角部分的斗拱。由于转角处的方向性，两个方向的构件还要与对角线方向的斜构件相交。是所有斗拱中构造最复杂的一科。（这个...........太复杂，目前不会.....）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/forum/pic/item/fa91f70a19d8bc3ea491b52a848ba61ea9d34541.jpg\"><br></p>\n<p>红色为柱头斗拱，橙色为柱间斗拱，黄色为转角斗拱。</p>\n<p>（以上为作者整理的资料 ...）</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 斗拱的实践：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"2\">&nbsp; 说这么多废话，建筑还是要建滴</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/5.gif\"><font size=\"2\"><br></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;我们今天还是要建一个小型斗拱，大家可以对比一下我第一次建的哈</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 但是我们一般都是做大型宫殿才用上斗拱，平常的小型建筑大家可以不建或建一个超mini的（因为一个斗拱太大且又费时）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FvQCZtfhmXx-ZFDCyGHH1fFNN-_b\"><br></p>\n<p>超mini</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>正经建筑</p>\n<p>起柱啦+栌斗</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/ForVSDgDOjRwhSJEr0SsHmLKdc6l\"></p>\n<p>泥道拱</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FkvSBNPUk5l-FnYcLw8xZlSAlTJo\"></p>\n<p>往上一挑</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FonD8gJryU9RFl4l6KW8tyS4EHsc\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fv05EMdmleaMS34BHHPvCe9RK-xr\"></p>\n<p>往外跳~~~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgcqvANulpuwbB1qstnLLBvFwfLb\"></p>\n<p>耍头+昂</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FthnCt93ritFg-wYY8ZaRkc-bHvk\"></p>\n<p>齐心拱</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fv_ZONstL-zWL1VEEQd4A2TFM2v9\"></p>\n<p>再搭上檩~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FlrExG7Vxp7cx9deOS-NbULbifYb\"></p>\n<p>修修细节</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhIciR6nThF_boDzgUz_BEuDS5Bp\"><br></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FvmpvSUiF0JXRNoQxMXRzJ63HUh0\"></p>\n<p>小型斗拱建好啦~\\()/~</p>\n<p>远眺</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqFF0odu6guGM2QHk0PsZkj7XM1L\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">柱间斗拱~~</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgnX0vmuoLUQNgeV16d42XEsCOil\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">熊孩子—徒手拆斗拱：</font></p>\n<p>斗拱分解图</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fq8vUkjI2_ticOZUoOyWs_R64UEP\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjLpUZV-5pCNqWHJV3rHb3IGhosn\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<font size=\"4\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; THANK FOR YOUR READING</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\"><font size=\"7\"><br></font></p>\n<p>日常3只猫~&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;BY尚冲&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1515299003,"created_at":1514792426,"n_views":429,"n_replies":10,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":true,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinn